==反應==
[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]稱譽模擬生命，評論道 "藉著巧妙地銜接娛樂與教育的橫溝，模擬生命帶出遺傳學最引人入勝一面，並讓任何有興趣的人都能接觸到它"。<ref name="eden199304">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=105 | title=Last one in the gene pool is a... | work=Computer Gaming World | date=1993-04 | accessdate=6 July 2014 | author=Eden, Maxwell | pages=56 | archive-date=2014-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702235842/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=105 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

1993年這個遊戲因"最佳模擬"獲得軟件出版協會的科迪獎。<ref name="cgw199305">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=106 | title=Awards - Thy Name Is Controversy | work=Computer Gaming World | date=1993-05 | accessdate=7 July 2014 | pages=146 | archive-date=2014-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702235910/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1993&pub=2&id=106 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

此外，Games Finder給與模擬生命滿分10分的7.0分。<ref>{{cite web|url =http://gameslikefinder.com/simlife-genetic-playground/|title =Simlife Genetic Playground Review - Games Finder|work =|access-date =2014-12-19|archive-date =2014-06-25|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140625021919/http://gameslikefinder.com/simlife-genetic-playground|dead-url =no}}</ref>

